overview: Frankie Goes To Hollywood: Their music videos told bizarre stories - from the overtly sexual sado club to the biblical nativity play. At the centre: Holly Johnson. Always with a slightly ironic charm and in a tailor-made suit. Always style-conscious, even in the crises of his life. At Baloise 2022  he revives the emotions of yesteryear with his British humour and his immortal solo hit "Americanos".
title: Holly Johnson - Baloise Session 2022
